reviewText: I have been looking for a reasonably priced set for quite a while...it's great to have found it finally...on Amazon.

Excellent series on US Space History. Beautiful narration by Sheen. Just one problem. This series has been out for
awhile. Why isn't it on DVD??
The original PBS documentary, contains excellent footage, and narration by Martin Sheen.  One problem I had: the most important tape (Apollo) was blank!
